pageContext.claim: “Let me tell you something: Biden’s son is corrupt, and Biden is corrupt. And I’d rather run against Biden than almost any of those candidates. And I think they're all weak. But I think Biden has never been a smart guy, and he’s less smart now than he ever was.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has no evidence to claim former vice president Joe Biden is "corrupt." Biden, unlike Trump, had disclosed decades of tax returns. Hunter Biden, one of his sons, did business deals that might not have come his way if he had not been a vice president's son, but the same could be said of Trump's adult children.
